#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "After almost two years of work, we are happy to announce the release of Xfce 4.20 !\n"
msgstr "約2年間の作業を経て、Xfce 4.20 のリリースを発表できることを嬉しく思います！\n"

#. type: Plain text
